        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nHi DeWayne, thanks for good point. First of all, the synchronized keyword in the getter is not even needed, because we only read the map. The collections is never modified, only read, so ConcurrentHashmap is not needed also. \nI used Collections.unmodifiableMap as you suggested.",
